title: Saint Laurent Small Le 5 a 7 Supple Bag
description: Saint Laurent small Le 5 A 7 supple bag in black finely grained leather. Featuring antique gold-toned hardware, a single flat adjustable shoulder strap and an open top secured by a fold over leather tab with signature YSL logo. The hook closure opens to a black suede interior with a zip pocket. Approximate dimensions: 22cm(L) x 21cm(H) x 9cm(D) and 20.5cm shoulder strap drop. Accompanied by a Saint Laurent dustbag. With Entrupy Certificate of Authenticity. (Pre-owned)
